
1.
Check if FTP is running: 

service vsftpd status 
CTRL C - quit. 

Open FireFox WB:
ftp://site1.com 

2.
Add FTP user:

adduser ftpuser1 

password: lowercase > password1 < 

systemctl restart vsftpd 

3.
cd /home/ftpuser1

ls

touch testing123456 

validation of users not disallowed:
vi or nano /etc/ftpusers 
